on.com/onl_info/images/575_filet.jpg" alt="filet" width="575" height="20" /><br /><span class="date">Vendredi 21 decembre - 15h00</span><br /><span class="Style1">Concert Expresso</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="Style2">SPANISH BRASS</span></p>\r\n<p class="Style1"><strong>Joan Baptista Cabanilles</strong>&nbsp;Batalla imperial (arr. Carlos Benet&oacute;)<br /><strong>Johann Sebastian Bach&nbsp;</strong>Aria des Variations Goldberg,&nbsp;<br />BWV 988 (arr. Carlos Benet&oacute;)<br /><strong>Johann Sebastian Bach</strong>&nbsp;Toccata et Fugue en r&eacute; mineur,&nbsp;<br />BWV 565 (arr. Fred Mills)<br /><strong>Vladimir Cosma</strong>&nbsp;Courts-m&eacute;trages</p>\r\n<p class="Style1">Spanish Brass Luur Metalls<br />Fran&ccedil;ois Castang, pr&eacute;sentation</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/images/575_filet.jpg" alt="filet" width="575" height="20" /><br /><span class="date">Dimanche 23 decembre - 11h00</span><br /><span class="Style1">Musique de chambre</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="Style2">NO&Euml;L CUIVRE</span></p>\r\n<p class="Style1"><strong>Dmitri Chostakovitch</strong>&nbsp;Ouverture de f&ecirc;te (arr. Pieter Lawrence)<br /><strong>Christian Lindberg</strong>&nbsp;Brain Rubbish<br /><strong>Astor Piazzolla</strong>&nbsp;Libertango (arr. Thierry Caens)<br /><strong>Sergue&iuml; Prokofiev</strong>&nbsp;Trois sc&egrave;nes de Rom&eacute;o et Juliette (arr. Joseph Kreines)<br /><strong>Lalo Schiffrin</strong>&nbsp;Mission impossible (arr. Calvin Custer)<br /><strong>Enrique Crespo</strong>&nbsp;Chants de No&euml;l.</p>\r\n<p class="Style1">Spanish Brass Luur Metalls<br />Cuivres de l&rsquo;Orchestre national de Lyon<br />Philippe Ferro, direction</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/images/575_filet.jpg" alt="filet" width="575" height="20" /><br /><span class="date">Samedi 29 decembre - 18h00</span><br /><span class="date">Dimanche 30 decembre - 16h00</span><br /><span class="date">Lundi 31 decembre - 20h00</sp