<span class="Style1"><strong>Samuel Barber</strong>&nbsp;Essai pour orchestre n&deg; 2, op. 17<br /><strong>George Gershwin</strong>&nbsp;Concerto pour piano en fa<br /><strong>Igor Stravinsky</strong>&nbsp;Le Sacre du Printemps<br /></span></p>\r\n<p class="Style1">Orchestre national de Lyon<br />Jean-Yves Thibaudet, piano<br />Leonard Slatkin, direction</p>\r\n<p class="Style1">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2"><img src="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/images/760_filet.jpg" alt="trait" width="760" height="20" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top"><a id="mai" name="mai"></a><span class="entree_txt_16">Mai</span></td>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<p><span class="date">Samedi 04 mai - 15h00</span>&nbsp;<span class="Style1"><a href="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/pages_saison/Bourse%20du%20travail.htm" target="_blank">(Bourse du travail)</a></span><br /><span class="Style1">Concert Jeune Public</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="Style2">SCHEHERAZADE</span></p>\r\n<p class="Style1"><strong>Nikola&iuml; Rimski-Korsakov</strong>&nbsp;Sch&eacute;h&eacute;razade, op. 35</p>\r\n<p class="Style1">Orchestre national de Lyon<br />Julien Masmondet, direction</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/images/575_filet.jpg" alt="filet" width="575" height="20" /><br /><span class="date">Dimanche 05 mai - 11h00</span>&nbsp;<span class="Style1"><a href="http://www.auditoriumlyon.com/onl_info/pages_saison/Bourse%20du%20travail.htm" target="_blank">(Bourse du travail)</a></span><br /><span class="Style1">Musique de chambre</span></p>\r\n<p><span class="Style2">AU COEUR DU ROMANTISME ALLEMAND</span></p>\r\n<p class="Style1"><strong>Robert Schumann</strong>&nbsp;Adagio et Allegro pour cor et piano op. 70<br />- Fantasiest&uuml;cke op. 73 (version pour hautbois d&rsquo;amour et piano)<br />- Dichterliebe (Les Amours d&rsquo;un po&egrave;te) op. 48 (extraits)<br /><strong>Carl Reinecke</strong>&nbsp;Trio pour hautbois, cor et piano en la m